          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " 10 mm thick copper and aluminum monitor foils,10 mm",
                "thick cadmium target foils and 100-500 mm thick",
                "aluminum degrader foils were irradiated. The foils,with",
                "an isotopic abundance and chemical purity of 99.9%,99%,",
                "99.7% and 99%,respectively.",
                "Isotopic composition of the natural cadmium foils-",
                "Cd-106-1.2%,Cd-108-0.9%,Cd-110-12.4%,Cd-111- 12.8%,",
                "Cd-112-24.0%,Cd-113 12.3%,Cd-114 28.8%,Cd-116 7.6%.",
                "Isotopic composition of the Cd-116 enriched product",
                "Cd-106-0.01%,Cd-108-0.01%,Cd-110-0.25%,Cd-111- 0.25%,",
                "Cd-112-0.71%,Cd-113 0.38%,Cd-114 1.79%,Cd-116 96.6%."
              ]
            }
          ],
